{"tid":839172,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何超蓮巴黎晒長腿：隨便拍都好看","createTime":"2018-09-27T17:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T17:21:30.000Z","uid":147522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"41eb4039efa3b596fd931e13e34f497b6787c23a","tid":839172,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/012125_8d864cb08d0125dbc702bf9065a85798.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F012125_8d864cb08d0125dbc702bf9065a85798.png&h=72e79075&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/012126_22e041a7abbf34306a2c6d7e575f100c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F012126_22e041a7abbf34306a2c6d7e575f100c.png&h=a3085e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日獲邀出席巴黎時裝周嘅賭王何鴻燊三房千金何超蓮，連日嚟都喺社交網分享咗唔少靚相。相信睇咗咁多Fashion show嘅超蓮，都增添咗唔少着衫嘅靈感，今日佢又喺網上分享喺街頭擺出chok甫相，見超蓮着上露膊衫配上一頭曲髮，大晒白滑長腿，甚有時尚感，佢仲話：「巴黎就是隨便拍都好看。」另外，仲見佢食法式田螺相，似乎佢呢個旅程正到爆呀！"}]}